n><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f9557b16785ce1aa290aeada07bc096fe820663","tid":1541692,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"佢個唇做過手術?"},{"pid":"6df86987ed2133e25fe6cfb4df323a828c6d4cab","tid":1541692,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f9557b16785ce1aa290aeada07bc096fe820663","tid":1541692,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"佢個唇做過手術?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rSPw9dZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrSPw9dZ.jpg&h=501213a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aabc6c4998e01847f9dbf185c8270019a07489f8","tid":1541692,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T20:29:52.000Z","msg":"好撚樣衰"},{"pid":"327a8585b5fb559ed855fa9b843f77c57f12b885","tid":1541692,"uid":152123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T21:58:54.000Z","msg":"yuna啊（眼濕濕地說）"},{"pid":"4ae6751f31cc4a048f69fd6ab3e95bed77bb2792","tid":1541692,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T22:10:03.000Z","msg":"呢個傻鳩上位真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208b3b38386940b2e8c1bb10cef209693ce11274","tid":1541692,"uid":34643,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T22:40:27.000Z","msg":"基本上見到佢同條女既一齊劇情都會飛, 尷尬到打冷震"},{"pid":"5c9ba262e7a64ea5cfb9a77193f2208cedbaae80","tid":1541692,"uid":34643,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"208b3b38386940b2e8c1bb10cef209693ce11274","tid":1541692,"uid":34643,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T22:40:27.000Z","msg":"基本上見到佢同條女既一齊劇情都會飛, 尷尬到打冷震"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T22:4